How To Install Power Protect:

1. Download the Power Protect script and install it in the ```/Users/x74353/Library/Application Scripts/com.if.Amphetamine/``` folder

2. Download the Power Protect configuration file and install it in the ```/private/etc/sudoers.d/``` folder
